casebody.data:
No. 1468,

Misc.

Whiteley v. Warden, Wyoming Penitentiary. Richard A. Mullens for petitioner. Sterling A. Case, Deputy Attorney General of Wyoming, and Jack Speight, Assistant Attorney General, for respondent.

C. A. 10th Cir. Motion for leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. Certiorari granted limited to issue of constitutionality of arrest and search, and case transferred to appellate docket.
